{"type":"FeatureCollection","properties":{"name":"Collection ISDeform (Hors Appel à Idées)","short":"Collections ISDeform","chapter":"Pour aller plus loin","reference":true},"features":[{"type":"Feature","properties":{"image":{"src":"/data/images/FRANCE.png","attribution":"Capture Google Earth"},"id":"urn:ogc:def:EOP:CNES::FRANCE:","name":"France","location":"France","description":"Le pré-traitement du chantier \"France\" du SNO <a href='https://www.isdeform.fr/' target='_blank'>ISDeform</a> est réalisé par le service FLATSIM, hors appel à projet.<br> Le traitement finalisé est en cours de réalisation à ISTerre (UGA) par ISDeform. les produits seront disponibles via une collection dédiée sur le catalogue FormaTerre.<br>Le chantier se focalise sur les applications tectoniques, hydrologiques, les glissements de terrain et des glaciers rocheux.<br>Il permet également le suivi de la compaction des bassins sédimentaires, des déformations associées à l'exploitation du sous-sol (stockage, mines, hydrothermalisme) et à certaines infrastructures (digues, etc.)","theme":[],"leaders":[""],"popup":"fmt-under","width":110},"geometry":{"type":"Polygon","coordinates":[[[-4.930353275492935,48.85330977010725],[-4.727254791671241,47.46437820332663],[-2.611099621529078,47.176109387579714],[-1.765947866271063,46.35061232430444],[-1.281132130696698,45.446496493098195],[-1.667674406357341,43.55964606275472],[-2.145938577937458,43.408960090887014],[-2.761785593396787,43.52688824278348],[-2.879713745293254,43.408960090887014],[-2.401449573713137,41.64658937643425],[-1.405611846587413,41.771069092324964],[-1.110791466846245,40.74902510922225],[-0.128056867709018,40.86695326111872],[-0.114953739720522,40.77523136519925],[0.861229295422458,40.9324689010612],[2.322228066139802,41.260047100773605],[3.278756409300037,41.784172220313465],[3.514612713092971,42.15761136798561],[3.167379821397818,42.62277241157723],[3.19358607737481,43.04207250720911],[4.025634704644329,43.42206321887551],[5.0083693